[gd_resource type="Theme" load_steps=14 format=3]

; EWSim shared UI theme (fx/) — the one instrument-chrome skin for every view's
; controls (buttons, sliders, labels, the control panel, tooltips), baked so current
; AND future views inherit it by setting `theme` on their root Control. PURE CHROME:
; display only. Palette matches Sandbox.gd's COL_* constants (deep navy panels, a
; cyan-blue accent, low-alpha borders).

